---
name: shopping_campaign_performance
description: >
  Get Google Shopping campaign performance from the Shopping Insider BigQuery
  datasets. Returns per-campaign impressions, clicks, cost, conversions,
  conversion value, CTR, CPC and ROAS over a date range. Use to answer "how
  are my Shopping campaigns doing this week / last 30 days".
---
Use for time-bounded Shopping campaign performance questions.
